title: Week 6 Preview & Falcons vs. Saints recap
itunes:title: Week 6 Preview & Falcons vs. Saints recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler - welcome in NFL Media's Andrew Siciliano as they break down each Week 6 matchup. Then, the heroes recap the Saints 31-21 victory over the Falcons, giving Atlanta its first loss of the season.
